scripts.generate:ts: openapi-generator-cli generate -i specs/openapi.json -g typescript-axios -c configs/typescript.json -o clients/typescript
scripts.generate:java: openapi-generator-cli generate -i specs/openapi.json -g java -c configs/java.json -o clients/java
scripts.generate:python: openapi-generator-cli generate -i specs/openapi.json -g python -c configs/python.json -o clients/python
scripts.generate:all: npm run generate:ts && npm run generate:java && npm run generate:python && npm run enhance
